The Image Element: Adding images to our website

<img src="url" alt="Alternative URL name"/>

# SRC
# Attribute is called source or src and this renders the image. 
# SRC tells the image element what is the source of the image, therefore value is the location (url) of the image. 
# Image element is a void element so no closing tag needed

# ALT
# Alternative Text Description, useful for people with visual impairments so this desctiption of the image can be read out to them. 